        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/n/8c91f0/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-07-27T02:17:39.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"153678\">\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>2012 Serge Dagueneau C\u00f4tes de la Charit\u00e9 Les Mont\u00e9es de St. Lay Pinot Beurrot</strong> \u2013 hints of chard as well as sauv blanc in this nose, slightly funky, some shortbread cookie elements, finishing with a buttery sort of feel. Pinot Beurrot is the Burgundian name for Pinot Gris.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>If I\u2019ve got the correct \u201cSaint Lay\u201d, then it\u2019s in the hills, upstream of Sancerre &amp; Pouilly.</p>\n<p>Latitude-wise, it lines up with Gevrey Chambertin or Fixin [to the east].<br>\n.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/3/d/3d24cb674f1fa2baa1e95b45c8d75f7f3c40fc39.png\" data-download-href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/3d24cb674f1fa2baa1e95b45c8d75f7f3c40fc39\" title=\"saint-lay_LONGITUDE.png\"><img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/3/d/3d24cb674f1fa2baa1e95b45c8d75f7f3c40fc39_2_690x390.png\" alt=\"saint-lay_LONGITUDE.png\" data-base62-sha1=\"8ITXnc25h21QzdXCLLk8UNrBiPL\" width=\"690\" height=\"390\" srcset=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/3/d/3d24cb674f1fa2baa1e95b45c8d75f7f3c40fc39_2_690x390.png, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/3/d/3d24cb674f1fa2baa1e95b45c8d75f7f3c40fc39_2_1035x585.png 1.5x, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/3/d/3d24cb674f1fa2baa1e95b45c8d75f7f3c40fc39_2_1380x780.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"EBEDE5\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">saint-lay_LONGITUDE.png</span><span class=\"informations\">3723\u00d72107 610 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>\n.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/3/0/300aca0f4d12b3c67ad7d5d8f8f0c6a3a484c414.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/300aca0f4d12b3c67ad7d5d8f8f0c6a3a484c414\" title=\"saint-lay_LATITUDE.jpg\"><img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/3/0/300aca0f4d12b3c67ad7d5d8f8f0c6a3a484c414_2_690x198.jpeg\" alt=\"saint-lay_LATITUDE.jpg\" data-base62-sha1=\"6R028MdT0XefHtkLnSgNzuK18DG\" width=\"690\" height=\"198\" srcset=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/3/0/300aca0f4d12b3c67ad7d5d8f8f0c6a3a484c414_2_690x198.jpeg, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/3/0/300aca0f4d12b3c67ad7d5d8f8f0c6a3a484c414_2_1035x297.jpeg 1.5x, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/3/0/300aca0f4d12b3c67ad7d5d8f8f0c6a3a484c414_2_1380x396.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"E6EFDB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">saint-lay_LATITUDE.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">3114\u00d7894 643 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>\n.<br>\nBut I might have the wrong \u201cSaint Lay\u201d.<br>\n.</p>",
